Check Readme and create notes for the instructions
Secure Users as mentioned in Readme

Execute commands to get the scripts from our repo & execute
------------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install git-all
git clone https://github.com/guptaanisha/SecureDebian.git
cd SecureDebian/Debian
ls -l *.sh
chmod 755 *.sh
sudo ./deb_installPackages.sh
sudo ./secure_deb_system.sh
sudo ./secure_ssh.sh
sudo ./secure_firewall.sh

